window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Logan Gyre is king of Cenaria, a country under siege, with a threadbare army and little hope. He has one chance - a desperate gamble, but one that could destroy his kingdom.</p> <p>In the north, the new Godking has a plan. If it comes to fruition, no one will have the power to stop him.</p> <p>Kylar Stern has no choice. To save his friends - and perhaps his enemies - he must accomplish the impossible: assassinate a goddess.</p> <p>Performed by Dylan Lynch, Eric Messner, Laura Quinn, Ren Casey, Ken Jackson, Christopher Graybill, Michael Glenn, Terence Aselford, Tim Getman, MB Van Dorn, Elizabeth Jernigan, Richard Rohan, Colleen Delany, Johann Dettweiler, Thomas Penny, Joe Brack, Casie Platt, Nanette Savard, Lily Beacon, Mort Shelby, James Lewis, Scott McCormick, Yazmin Tuazon.</p>"; 
